WEBVTT

01:43.070 --> 01:45.960
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.100 --> 01:48.990
[Episode 25]

01:55.810 --> 01:57.600
Let me stay by your side.

02:35.990 --> 02:37.890
[Hiroshima Mon Amour]

02:38.130 --> 02:39.340
164.

02:41.210 --> 02:42.540
[164]

03:08.910 --> 03:10.380
[Spare no effort today, ensure perfection tomorrow.]

03:19.510 --> 03:20.150
Sorry,

03:20.190 --> 03:20.940
I'm late.

03:23.190 --> 03:24.250
Where were you?

03:24.829 --> 03:26.870
I went to a book club today.

03:26.900 --> 03:28.190
They happened to be discussing

03:28.230 --> 03:29.310
"Hiroshima Mon Amour"

03:29.329 --> 03:30.329
by Marguerite Duras.

03:31.010 --> 03:31.850
I was going to

03:32.040 --> 03:34.060
ask you to come with me.

03:37.680 --> 03:38.620
I'm sorry, Man.

03:39.990 --> 03:40.630
I can't take you

03:40.630 --> 03:42.240
to movie theaters

03:42.350 --> 03:43.440
and amusement parks

03:43.560 --> 03:44.520
like your classmates do.

03:45.870 --> 03:47.500
You have to settle for places like this.

03:47.910 --> 03:48.579
Not at all.

03:49.280 --> 03:49.829
Being able to do this,

03:49.829 --> 03:51.430
I'm already more than happy.

04:20.279 --> 04:21.170
Happy birthday.

04:30.300 --> 04:31.390
How did you know

04:31.430 --> 04:33.000
today is my birthday?

04:35.330 --> 04:36.970
I looked it up.

04:41.030 --> 04:41.790
I also know

04:42.710 --> 04:43.350
you've always spent it

04:43.350 --> 04:44.390
alone in the past.

04:46.230 --> 04:46.990
From now on,

04:47.590 --> 04:48.520
I'll spend it with you.

04:52.190 --> 04:52.870
Thank you.

04:55.510 --> 04:56.430
Make a wish.

05:12.710 --> 05:14.130
What do you want for your birthday?

05:19.910 --> 05:21.840
I usually read it

05:21.870 --> 05:23.320
quietly in the library,

05:23.870 --> 05:25.030
but today,

05:25.990 --> 05:27.110
I want you to read it to me.

05:36.990 --> 05:39.530
"I once had the misfortune

05:39.560 --> 05:40.720
of being utterly humiliated.

05:42.630 --> 05:44.400
The razor at my head.

05:44.550 --> 05:45.880
From this foolish act,

05:45.909 --> 05:47.710
I gained extraordinary wisdom.

05:48.430 --> 05:50.480
I want to have lived through that moment.

05:50.710 --> 05:53.470
That incomparable moment.

05:55.550 --> 05:56.310
He speaks,

05:56.360 --> 05:57.909
as though divorced from the present.

05:58.780 --> 06:00.850
He: In a few years,

06:01.470 --> 06:02.870
when I'll have forgotten you,

06:04.190 --> 06:05.750
and when other such adventures,

06:05.950 --> 06:07.920
from sheer habit, will happen to me,

06:08.990 --> 06:10.110
I'll remember you

06:10.990 --> 06:11.870
as the symbol

06:11.870 --> 06:13.070
of love's forgetfulness.

06:14.470 --> 06:15.400
I'll think of

06:15.430 --> 06:16.710
this adventure

06:17.160 --> 06:18.950
as of the horror of oblivion.

06:20.270 --> 06:21.510
I already know it.

06:22.030 --> 06:23.110
I'll do that."

06:29.430 --> 06:30.250
What's wrong?

06:32.970 --> 06:34.560
No matter what happens in the future,

06:35.330 --> 06:37.030
whether we have one or not,

06:37.590 --> 06:38.520
the moment

06:38.630 --> 06:39.900
just now

06:39.920 --> 06:42.400
is the most special

06:43.430 --> 06:44.790
and happiest of my life.

06:47.840 --> 06:48.810
Thank you.

07:04.830 --> 07:05.550
I love you.

07:11.950 --> 07:12.830
I love you too.

07:27.670 --> 07:28.990
Where was I?

07:30.660 --> 07:31.630
"I meet you."

07:34.870 --> 07:35.909
"I meet you.

07:36.350 --> 07:37.350
I remember you.

07:38.560 --> 07:39.790
This city

07:40.450 --> 07:42.920
was made to the size of love."

08:34.650 --> 08:36.940
Why did you film me?

08:36.970 --> 08:38.730
Stay away from me!

08:42.030 --> 08:43.450
You're causing such a scene.

08:43.970 --> 08:45.780
Aren't you afraid the whole school will find out?

08:47.540 --> 08:49.120
Then Coach Zhou's life

08:49.160 --> 08:50.660
would be completely ruined by you.

08:53.950 --> 08:54.710
You want to smash it?

08:54.850 --> 08:55.550
Go ahead.

08:55.570 --> 08:56.890
I have more than one copy.

08:57.030 --> 08:58.120
But think it through.

08:58.910 --> 09:00.640
This phone is expensive.

09:01.030 --> 09:02.430
Can you afford to pay it

09:02.960 --> 09:04.160
with your student loan?

09:06.430 --> 09:07.030
What...

09:08.710 --> 09:11.910
W-What do you want?

09:12.510 --> 09:15.000
I want you to pretend to fall in love with Jiang Chengyi

09:15.540 --> 09:17.270
and break up Lu Yan and Jiang Chengyi.

09:19.110 --> 09:19.910
Impossible.

09:19.920 --> 09:21.120
In your dreams!

09:22.460 --> 09:24.030
In my dreams?

09:24.430 --> 09:25.190
That's right.

09:25.580 --> 09:27.700
I've been dreaming all along.

09:27.820 --> 09:28.830
But look,

09:29.960 --> 09:30.590
my dream

09:30.630 --> 09:31.910
is about to come true.

09:43.100 --> 09:45.050
I don't have much patience.

09:47.080 --> 09:48.270
If you've made up your mind,

09:48.290 --> 09:49.030
come to the small garden

09:49.070 --> 09:50.820
behind the teaching building tomorrow.

09:51.830 --> 09:53.600
I'll teach you what to do.

09:57.430 --> 09:58.230
Do as Ding Jing said.

10:01.470 --> 10:02.590
Impossible.

10:02.810 --> 10:04.070
I would never, ever do anything

10:04.070 --> 10:05.660
to hurt Yan.

10:05.700 --> 10:07.340
Then what should we do?

10:07.620 --> 10:08.590
If she makes that video

10:08.630 --> 10:09.360
public,

10:10.230 --> 10:11.150
I'll be branded

10:11.190 --> 10:12.350
as a hypocrite,

10:12.460 --> 10:13.230
and you'll be labeled

10:13.270 --> 10:14.430
as a homewrecker that everyone despises.

10:15.250 --> 10:16.350
Even if I don't care,

10:16.390 --> 10:17.470
you're still so young.

10:17.530 --> 10:18.710
With that kind of reputation,

10:18.750 --> 10:19.990
how are you going to move forward?

10:20.870 --> 10:22.750
I don't want that for you either.

10:22.830 --> 10:23.870
Listen to me, Man.

10:25.350 --> 10:26.550
W-We don't really need

10:26.600 --> 10:27.670
to break them up.

10:28.510 --> 10:29.910
We'll just put on a show,

10:30.140 --> 10:31.380
making Ding Jing think

10:31.400 --> 10:32.830
she's won,

10:33.350 --> 10:33.910
so she'll destroy

10:33.910 --> 10:34.910
that video.

10:35.560 --> 10:36.200
Okay?

10:37.480 --> 10:38.320
A show?

10:38.710 --> 10:39.200
Yes.

10:39.630 --> 10:40.400
Once Ding Jing

10:40.510 --> 10:41.720
destroys the video

10:41.750 --> 10:42.670
and this all blows over,

10:43.380 --> 10:44.390
we'll go apologize

10:45.190 --> 10:46.430
and find a way to make it up to them.

10:48.510 --> 10:49.660
I'll do it with you.

10:50.550 --> 10:51.310
But...

10:52.550 --> 10:53.750
I still can't

10:53.750 --> 10:56.450
hurt Yan for myself.

10:58.190 --> 10:59.350
You're each other's best friend,

10:59.460 --> 11:00.000
right?

11:00.790 --> 11:02.330
You don't want to hurt her,

11:02.710 --> 11:03.830
and she wouldn't want to see you

11:03.830 --> 11:04.790
suffer like this either.

11:05.530 --> 11:06.550
Once it's over

11:06.550 --> 11:07.270
and she knows the truth,

11:07.270 --> 11:08.310
she'll forgive you.

11:09.860 --> 11:10.720
Really?

11:15.350 --> 11:16.190
But...

11:17.350 --> 11:18.540
Just do it for me.

11:22.480 --> 11:23.190
For us.

11:25.110 --> 11:25.710
Okay?

11:38.750 --> 11:39.270
Then I'll…

11:39.270 --> 11:39.910
I'll go.

11:40.920 --> 11:41.830
You're alright?

11:42.190 --> 11:43.190
Call me if you need anything.

12:28.030 --> 12:30.360
Let's put an end to this.

12:31.730 --> 12:33.030
I can't keep doing things

12:33.030 --> 12:34.470
that hurt Yan and Jiang Chengyi.

12:34.470 --> 12:36.110
I'd rather die.

12:40.580 --> 12:41.510
I understand.

12:44.950 --> 12:45.630
Sorry.

12:45.630 --> 12:46.460
I shouldn't have pushed you

12:46.510 --> 12:47.700
to do something you didn't want to.

12:51.800 --> 12:53.740
This is my responsibility.

12:54.500 --> 12:56.240
I was out of my mind.

12:57.890 --> 12:58.990
I can't believe I asked you,

12:59.030 --> 13:00.750
a young girl, to cover for me.

13:02.030 --> 13:03.590
I'm such a jerk.

13:07.030 --> 13:08.350
Stop, stop.

13:08.370 --> 13:09.020
Stop.

13:17.700 --> 13:18.830
I'm sorry, Man.

13:20.350 --> 13:21.190
I'm useless.

13:25.470 --> 13:26.990
I really don't know what to do.

13:30.770 --> 13:32.350
If they ever ask you,

13:33.830 --> 13:35.390
just say I forced you.

13:38.070 --> 13:39.030
My life can't

13:39.030 --> 13:39.870
get any better anyway.

13:42.060 --> 13:43.270
But you're different.

13:44.910 --> 13:46.040
You're still young.

13:46.990 --> 13:48.190
You still have a future.

13:50.670 --> 13:51.790
You deserve a good life.

13:58.710 --> 14:00.070
I'll protect you.

14:04.190 --> 14:05.190
What are you planning to do?

14:08.830 --> 14:09.350
I…

14:10.550 --> 14:11.800
I can't tell you

14:11.830 --> 14:12.830
what I'm going to do now,

14:13.790 --> 14:15.190
but I promise

14:15.390 --> 14:16.350
that after this,

14:16.350 --> 14:17.230
Ding Jing will never

14:17.270 --> 14:18.390
threaten us again,

14:18.410 --> 14:19.470
and she'll never hurt

14:19.470 --> 14:21.110
Yan and Jiang Chengyi again.

14:23.030 --> 14:24.120
What are you going to do?

14:24.710 --> 14:25.510
Tell me.

14:26.580 --> 14:27.860
I'll do it with you.

14:29.430 --> 14:29.950
No.

14:31.430 --> 14:33.110
You don't need to do anything.

14:34.470 --> 14:35.430
I told you,

14:36.390 --> 14:37.080
I want us

14:37.110 --> 14:38.470
to always be together.

14:39.670 --> 14:40.310
For that,

14:41.390 --> 14:42.960
I'm willing to give everything.

14:50.310 --> 14:59.400
[Spare no effort today, ensure perfection tomorrow.]

15:02.180 --> 15:11.670
[Spare no effort today, ensure perfection tomorrow.]

15:14.940 --> 15:19.120
[Spare no effort today, ensure perfection tomorrow.]

15:34.830 --> 15:36.070
Dear leaders and teachers,

15:36.070 --> 15:36.750
hello.

15:37.070 --> 15:38.790
Deng Man, a 2014 Advanced Nursing student

15:38.830 --> 15:39.430
from the School of Medicine,

15:39.450 --> 15:40.930
died in an accident yesterday.

15:41.060 --> 15:42.070
Starting today,

15:42.110 --> 15:44.120
the police will conduct an investigation on campus.

15:44.230 --> 15:45.200
If any teacher

15:45.230 --> 15:46.470
can offer any clues,

15:46.510 --> 15:47.950
please contact the administrative office immediately.

15:48.010 --> 15:48.630
Thank you.

16:01.350 --> 16:03.350
I want us to always be together.

16:04.070 --> 16:05.030
For that,

16:05.910 --> 16:07.830
I'm willing to give everything.

16:37.290 --> 16:39.610
[Library]

16:38.870 --> 16:39.670
Coach Zhou.

16:40.390 --> 16:40.990
Principal.

16:42.110 --> 16:42.970
Officers.

16:43.030 --> 16:44.550
[Hiroshima Mon Amour]

16:43.070 --> 16:44.900
This is Coach Zhou Zhicheng.

16:44.970 --> 16:45.950
He's been a PE teacher

16:45.990 --> 16:47.480
at our university for many years,

16:47.500 --> 16:48.480
and he's

16:48.510 --> 16:49.710
the Model of Morality this year.

16:49.790 --> 16:50.310
Zhou,

16:50.320 --> 16:51.030
did you

16:51.030 --> 16:52.770
see the message from the administrative office?

16:53.470 --> 16:54.350
Yes.

16:54.870 --> 16:55.690
Coach Zhou,

16:55.790 --> 16:57.230
do you know that girl?

16:58.600 --> 16:59.830
She was one of my students.

17:00.030 --> 17:01.820
What sport did she take for PE?

17:03.470 --> 17:04.480
Volleyball.

17:04.599 --> 17:05.520
Did you have

17:05.589 --> 17:07.099
any private interactions with her?

17:08.670 --> 17:09.430
No.

17:11.630 --> 17:12.990
[Hiroshima Mon Amour]

17:19.010 --> 17:20.619
I've thought about

17:22.790 --> 17:24.470
destroying this book many times.

17:27.890 --> 17:29.290
But I couldn't bring myself to do it.

17:31.270 --> 17:32.110
It holds all

17:32.110 --> 17:33.160
my memories with her.

17:34.820 --> 17:35.790
I couldn't let it go.

17:41.530 --> 17:43.140
I really loved her.

17:44.910 --> 17:45.990
How did you love her?

17:47.310 --> 17:48.420
You loved her,

17:48.720 --> 17:50.710
yet you watched as Ding Jing bullied her.

17:51.310 --> 17:51.950
You loved her,

17:51.990 --> 17:52.790
yet you forced her

17:52.830 --> 17:54.350
to confess to Jiang Chengyi,

17:55.590 --> 17:56.260
even though you knew

17:56.310 --> 17:57.760
the person she liked was you.

17:58.010 --> 17:59.860
You're so much older than her.

17:59.890 --> 18:01.150
Even if what Man did

18:01.190 --> 18:02.110
was not right,

18:02.190 --> 18:03.750
shouldn't you have told her

18:03.790 --> 18:05.350
to stop before it went too far?

18:06.220 --> 18:07.390
How could you just sit back

18:07.430 --> 18:08.780
and let it all happen?

18:09.280 --> 18:10.560
Do you know that

18:10.990 --> 18:11.750
Deng Man

18:12.150 --> 18:13.430
never revealed your relationship

18:13.430 --> 18:14.590
even before she died?

18:15.630 --> 18:17.330
We even called you a teacher.

18:17.590 --> 18:18.940
How could you do that to Deng Man?

18:19.010 --> 18:20.360
How could you do that to your wife?

18:20.390 --> 18:21.230
Do you deserve

18:21.260 --> 18:22.230
to be called a teacher?

18:23.190 --> 18:24.050
Calm down.

18:25.180 --> 18:26.930
Let him make things clear.

18:33.490 --> 18:34.740
You're right.

18:38.150 --> 18:39.430
I'm a jerk,

18:41.110 --> 18:42.990
and karma has caught up with me.

18:46.140 --> 18:48.010
I was diagnosed with cancer three years ago.

18:50.300 --> 18:51.810
I don't think I have much time left.

18:53.640 --> 18:54.610
But I thought,

18:56.610 --> 18:58.090
if I died too,

19:00.270 --> 19:01.370
then no one would ever

19:02.990 --> 19:04.760
bring up Man's case again.

19:08.410 --> 19:09.820
So I wrote an anonymous letter

19:10.750 --> 19:12.270
to the police.

19:12.790 --> 19:14.030
You wrote that letter?

19:17.510 --> 19:18.360
Back then, the letter claimed

19:18.380 --> 19:19.620
that Deng Man didn't commit suicide.

19:20.790 --> 19:21.830
Do you have any evidence

19:21.830 --> 19:22.910
or leads?

19:25.480 --> 19:26.750
I don't have any evidence.

19:29.080 --> 19:30.080
But I know

19:30.110 --> 19:31.710
she'd never have committed suicide.

19:38.040 --> 19:39.590
We were so in love.

19:40.750 --> 19:41.950
She'd never have had the heart

19:41.990 --> 19:43.510
to leave me behind like that.

19:43.650 --> 19:45.420
She definitely didn't commit suicide.

19:56.660 --> 19:58.600
We've figured out where the money came from

19:59.370 --> 20:01.070
and what happened between them back then.

20:03.170 --> 20:04.930
But something still feels off.

20:07.710 --> 20:08.800
What do you think…

20:11.310 --> 20:12.110
is off?

20:16.920 --> 20:18.030
I can't say for sure.

20:18.270 --> 20:19.380
I'll think about it after I get back.

20:20.200 --> 20:21.760
His story

20:22.470 --> 20:23.910
is too perfect.

21:00.720 --> 21:01.860
I've already

21:02.630 --> 21:04.130
done everything you asked.

21:24.360 --> 21:25.430
Don't worry.

21:25.840 --> 21:27.150
I won't let anyone know

21:27.170 --> 21:28.180
about your existence.

21:52.110 --> 21:53.000
Yan.

21:59.850 --> 22:00.560
Man.

22:08.830 --> 22:10.350
I finally see you again.

22:11.240 --> 22:12.640
I've missed you so much.

22:13.790 --> 22:14.910
I've missed you too.

22:18.360 --> 22:19.940
You and Jiang Chengyi made up?

22:24.040 --> 22:24.790
That's wonderful.

22:30.110 --> 22:30.950
Man,

22:32.550 --> 22:33.590
there's something I've always

22:33.590 --> 22:35.550
wanted to ask you.

22:40.470 --> 22:41.350
Do you regret it?

22:41.750 --> 22:43.220
Of course, I do.

22:43.910 --> 22:45.070
I lost the two people

22:45.090 --> 22:46.730
I loved most in my life at the same time.

22:50.830 --> 22:52.070
I was too young back then.

22:52.800 --> 22:54.680
I didn't really understand what love was.

22:55.720 --> 22:56.630
When I needed care

22:56.670 --> 22:57.400
the most,

22:57.400 --> 22:58.470
he appeared,

22:58.620 --> 22:59.230
and

22:59.550 --> 23:00.870
he treated me very well.

23:04.800 --> 23:05.770
But compared with that,

23:06.030 --> 23:07.480
what I regret more…

23:09.640 --> 23:10.350
is not telling you

23:10.390 --> 23:12.190
about my relationship with him.

23:15.350 --> 23:16.550
You'll forgive me,

23:17.890 --> 23:18.530
won't you?

23:27.950 --> 23:28.920
You must believe

23:28.920 --> 23:30.190
in your choice.

23:30.640 --> 23:32.620
Jiang Chengyi really loves you.

23:33.230 --> 23:33.910
And,

23:34.630 --> 23:36.370
from now on,

23:36.630 --> 23:37.960
you need to be happy every single day.

24:30.310 --> 24:31.870
I dreamed about Deng Man.

24:33.320 --> 24:35.090
She told me she was sorry.

24:35.140 --> 24:36.300
♫As the city flickers♫

24:37.840 --> 24:40.620
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

24:39.530 --> 24:40.570
It's in the past.

24:40.600 --> 24:41.460
Don't think about it.

24:41.900 --> 24:43.190
♫And you, who love to smile♫

24:43.630 --> 24:44.670
Get some more sleep.

24:44.210 --> 24:46.670
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

24:47.680 --> 24:50.040
♫The humor of time♫

24:51.530 --> 24:53.970
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

24:55.040 --> 24:57.190
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

24:57.470 --> 24:58.300
Everyone's busy?

25:00.180 --> 25:00.750
Jiang,

25:00.830 --> 25:01.550
your takeout.

25:03.510 --> 25:04.430
I didn't order any takeout.

25:08.870 --> 25:10.460
Panda love bento?

25:10.510 --> 25:11.360
What's that?

25:13.370 --> 25:14.430
Dr. Lu?

25:14.460 --> 25:15.260
Let me see.

25:16.640 --> 25:17.530
Are you dating someone?

25:18.410 --> 25:19.630
What is it? Let me see.

25:19.670 --> 25:21.100
Not unless you admit it.

25:21.310 --> 25:22.400
Let me see!

25:25.470 --> 25:26.510
You're dating someone, aren't you?

25:27.470 --> 25:28.280
Teach me how.

25:28.310 --> 25:29.150
I want to date too.

25:29.190 --> 25:30.370
I'm still single, Jiang.

25:30.420 --> 25:31.590
What can I teach you? Figure it out yourself.

25:31.590 --> 25:32.350
How can I teach you that?

25:32.390 --> 25:33.510
I want to date too.

25:33.790 --> 25:34.680
What's wrong with you?

25:34.710 --> 25:35.510
I can't teach you that.

25:35.540 --> 25:36.300
Get back to work.

25:39.130 --> 25:40.270
Panda love bento.

25:40.270 --> 25:41.310
Keep it down. Why are you so loud?

26:00.670 --> 26:03.790
[Thanks for the love bento.]

26:07.440 --> 26:11.240
[Stairs]

26:14.310 --> 26:14.950
Thanks

26:14.990 --> 26:16.030
for the love bento.

26:35.260 --> 26:37.890
[Huiting Complex]

26:40.640 --> 26:41.730
You didn't turn the lights off when you left?

26:42.070 --> 26:42.990
I did.

26:43.420 --> 26:44.500
Then why are the lights on?

26:56.510 --> 26:57.190
Mom?

26:58.930 --> 26:59.610
Auntie.

26:59.660 --> 27:00.500
Hello, Auntie.

27:00.590 --> 27:01.630
-Hello, Auntie.
-Mom.

27:01.850 --> 27:03.200
Why are you here?

27:03.230 --> 27:04.240
What?

27:05.230 --> 27:06.540
Did I come at a bad time?

27:06.560 --> 27:07.460
No,

27:07.640 --> 27:08.770
but if you'd told me in advance,

27:08.800 --> 27:10.120
I could've picked you up.

27:11.470 --> 27:13.370
You've already met his parents.

27:13.390 --> 27:15.100
Of course I had to hurry back to check things out.

27:15.320 --> 27:16.240
Listen.

27:16.260 --> 27:17.100
There are a few places

27:17.100 --> 27:17.870
I haven't visited.

27:17.890 --> 27:18.760
You'll need to reimburse me.

27:19.110 --> 27:19.510
Okay.

27:19.550 --> 27:20.720
No problem.

27:21.050 --> 27:22.470
Why have you lost weight?

27:22.550 --> 27:23.270
No.

27:23.290 --> 27:23.850
Look at you.

27:23.880 --> 27:24.840
You must've been through a lot.

27:24.860 --> 27:26.300
What are you talking about? I…

27:26.550 --> 27:28.170
I-I've been really happy.

27:28.180 --> 27:29.520
This, uh, this is…

27:29.590 --> 27:30.110
Auntie.

27:30.110 --> 27:30.430
Mom.

27:30.470 --> 27:30.950
Nice to meet you.

27:31.050 --> 27:31.890
Jiang Chengyi.

27:31.990 --> 27:33.470
-Well.
-Hello, Auntie.

27:34.750 --> 27:36.270
Jiang, right?

27:36.590 --> 27:37.110
Yeah.

27:38.190 --> 27:39.140
You're in great shape

27:40.090 --> 27:41.140
and pretty tall too.

27:41.920 --> 27:43.070
What are you, 190 cm?

27:43.100 --> 27:43.700
Not quite,

27:43.750 --> 27:44.390
just over 180 cm.

27:45.070 --> 27:45.830
See?

27:46.510 --> 27:47.950
Mom's got a good eye.

27:48.290 --> 27:48.980
Definitely.

27:49.780 --> 27:51.460
A-Are you two living together?

27:54.430 --> 27:55.030
No.

27:55.110 --> 27:55.910
-No.
-Auntie.

27:55.950 --> 27:57.570
I live next door.

27:57.680 --> 27:58.390
-And…
-Yeah.

27:58.660 --> 28:00.280
We run into each other

28:00.300 --> 28:01.440
going to and from work,

28:01.540 --> 28:02.720
and sometimes…

28:02.750 --> 28:03.430
We grab a meal together.

28:03.450 --> 28:03.830
Yeah.

28:03.830 --> 28:04.830
We sometimes have meals together.

28:05.330 --> 28:06.750
How's that different from living together?

28:07.000 --> 28:08.300
With those long legs of yours,

28:08.320 --> 28:09.670
one step from your balcony

28:09.710 --> 28:10.470
and you'd be here.

28:10.750 --> 28:11.640
No way.

28:11.870 --> 28:12.950
Mom, stop joking.

28:12.950 --> 28:13.710
It's the sixth floor.

28:13.710 --> 28:14.510
Who in their right mind

28:14.510 --> 28:15.550
would do that?

28:16.840 --> 28:17.750
Have you eaten yet?

28:17.890 --> 28:19.660
Why don't we order takeout?

28:19.910 --> 28:21.430
You're always eating takeout, aren't you?

28:21.550 --> 28:23.190
No wonder you've lost weight.

28:23.210 --> 28:24.570
Takeout is unhealthy.

28:24.670 --> 28:26.360
-Don't order takeout.
-Alright, no takeout.

28:26.380 --> 28:28.130
Since your mom's just arrived,

28:28.160 --> 28:29.140
let's go out for dinner.

28:29.430 --> 28:29.870
What do you think?

28:29.870 --> 28:30.710
Okay. Do you want to eat out?

28:30.730 --> 28:31.520
Nah.

28:32.170 --> 28:33.350
I'm tired after traveling.

28:33.630 --> 28:34.550
Let's just eat at home.

28:35.590 --> 28:36.110
Okay.

28:36.140 --> 28:36.840
Let's eat at home.

28:36.870 --> 28:37.730
We've got food anyway.

28:37.910 --> 28:38.910
Sit with your mom for a bit.

28:38.910 --> 28:39.990
I-I'll cook.

28:41.310 --> 28:41.790
Alright.

28:41.830 --> 28:42.470
Have a rest.

28:42.470 --> 28:43.350
Auntie, I'll cook.

28:43.350 --> 28:43.550
Okay.

28:43.710 --> 28:44.190
Okay.

28:44.430 --> 28:44.900
Mom.

28:47.130 --> 28:47.830
Mom.

28:49.550 --> 28:50.390
Okay.

28:51.230 --> 28:52.890
He's a great cook.

28:54.780 --> 28:56.130
He looks quite at home.

28:58.090 --> 28:58.940
He…

29:02.230 --> 29:03.030
Here.

29:03.070 --> 29:04.390
Be careful.

29:05.710 --> 29:07.070
Thank you.

29:07.470 --> 29:08.110
The dishes are all here.

29:08.590 --> 29:09.430
Eat up.

29:10.270 --> 29:10.670
Mom,

29:10.670 --> 29:11.830
try the beef first.

29:12.290 --> 29:13.330
It's a secret family recipe.

29:13.510 --> 29:14.270
It's really good.

29:17.300 --> 29:17.830
How is it?

29:19.470 --> 29:20.310
Not bad.

29:20.700 --> 29:21.820
The beef is really tender.

29:22.340 --> 29:23.350
Secret family recipe.

29:24.270 --> 29:25.020
You like it?

29:28.670 --> 29:29.450
Delicious.

29:29.550 --> 29:30.220
Sit down.

29:30.700 --> 29:31.630
I won't eat with you.

29:32.970 --> 29:34.230
Oh, my memory's terrible.

29:34.250 --> 29:35.730
What's your name again?

29:36.240 --> 29:37.530
I'm Jiang Chengyi, Auntie.

29:38.800 --> 29:40.020
Jiang Chengyi?

29:40.310 --> 29:40.830
Right.

29:40.950 --> 29:43.020
Why does your name sound so familiar?

29:44.000 --> 29:45.190
Sit down and eat.

29:45.190 --> 29:45.710
I'm good.

29:45.710 --> 29:46.470
Well,

29:46.540 --> 29:47.790
your mom just got here today.

29:48.030 --> 29:49.430
You two have a chat.

29:49.450 --> 29:50.480
I'll head back now.

29:50.950 --> 29:51.870
Auntie, I'm leaving.

29:55.420 --> 29:56.560
Jiang.

29:58.110 --> 29:58.990
The clothes in the washing machine

29:59.030 --> 29:59.870
are yours, right?

30:03.460 --> 30:04.110
Yes.

30:04.260 --> 30:05.460
I washed them for you.

30:05.490 --> 30:06.540
Don't forget to take them.

30:11.030 --> 30:12.080
Oh,

30:12.270 --> 30:13.240
thank you, Auntie.

30:17.190 --> 30:18.310
Thank you.

30:26.550 --> 30:27.990
Stop grinning!

31:07.120 --> 31:08.040
Mom,

31:08.530 --> 31:10.010
how long are you staying this time?

31:11.180 --> 31:11.910
Why?

31:12.550 --> 31:14.260
You think I'm in the way?

31:15.110 --> 31:15.860
No!

31:15.860 --> 31:17.630
Why are you always talking like that?

31:17.670 --> 31:19.940
I just want to know how long you're staying

31:19.990 --> 31:21.750
so I can decide if I should take time off to be with you.

31:22.870 --> 31:23.710
No need.

31:25.510 --> 31:26.850
I'm here for two things:

31:27.030 --> 31:27.580
one,

31:27.930 --> 31:28.680
to check out

31:28.750 --> 31:30.170
that boyfriend of yours next door;

31:30.610 --> 31:32.660
two, to get a health check at the hospital.

31:34.010 --> 31:34.960
I'll book it for you.

31:35.750 --> 31:36.730
No need.

31:36.950 --> 31:37.480
Dr. Han has

31:37.480 --> 31:38.430
already booked it for me.

31:42.950 --> 31:43.910
Tell me.

31:44.990 --> 31:46.470
How was the meeting

31:46.510 --> 31:47.420
with Jiang's parents?

31:47.750 --> 31:48.430
It went well.

31:48.430 --> 31:50.600
His parents really like me.

31:52.550 --> 31:54.760
I knew it'd be pointless to ask you!

31:54.790 --> 31:56.110
In your eyes,

31:56.230 --> 31:57.620
everyone's good.

31:59.860 --> 32:02.520
I just can't figure it out.

32:02.880 --> 32:03.670
For eight years,

32:03.710 --> 32:05.210
you didn't date anyone.

32:05.320 --> 32:06.910
Then all of a sudden,

32:06.930 --> 32:08.650
you've met his parents.

32:09.330 --> 32:11.170
How long have you two known each other?

32:11.390 --> 32:12.870
How long?

32:13.200 --> 32:15.120
We've known each other…

32:16.630 --> 32:17.830
for quite a while now.

32:18.620 --> 32:20.100
For quite a while?

32:21.920 --> 32:23.610
And you didn't tell me?

32:23.750 --> 32:24.550
You had me worrying about you

32:24.550 --> 32:25.790
every single day!

32:26.930 --> 32:28.420
I keep thinking about the days

32:28.460 --> 32:29.470
when you broke up

32:29.470 --> 32:31.250
with your ex

32:31.420 --> 32:32.740
and cried your heart out.

32:33.520 --> 32:34.290
Mom.

32:35.810 --> 32:36.610
Actually,

32:37.230 --> 32:38.700
he's

32:39.110 --> 32:40.460
my ex.

32:48.780 --> 32:50.580
I-I knew it.

32:50.610 --> 32:52.580
No wonder his name sounds so familiar.

32:53.070 --> 32:53.910
But honestly, Mom,

32:53.930 --> 32:55.330
it wasn't his fault back then.

32:55.400 --> 32:57.240
I was the one who ended things.

32:58.620 --> 32:59.440
Yan,

33:00.330 --> 33:01.950
it doesn't matter who ended things.

33:02.430 --> 33:03.430
The fact that you two

33:03.470 --> 33:04.940
broke up back then

33:04.940 --> 33:06.270
means you weren't

33:06.290 --> 33:07.560
right for each other.

33:07.750 --> 33:08.260
Mom,

33:08.310 --> 33:09.990
it was all just a misunderstanding back then.

33:10.010 --> 33:11.510
We've cleared it up,

33:11.630 --> 33:12.230
and we can finally

33:12.270 --> 33:13.520
be together again.

33:13.790 --> 33:14.430
And

33:14.470 --> 33:15.310
you know what?

33:15.720 --> 33:16.810
For these eight years,

33:16.840 --> 33:19.390
neither of us was with anyone else.

33:19.420 --> 33:20.260
We both waited for each other.

33:21.190 --> 33:22.090
Really?

33:28.940 --> 33:30.930
I believe in your judgment,

33:32.570 --> 33:33.530
but Yan…

33:33.990 --> 33:34.790
But…

33:35.950 --> 33:37.350
But you're worried about his job,

33:37.370 --> 33:38.090
aren't you?

33:39.360 --> 33:40.160
It's not that I think

33:40.200 --> 33:41.750
his job is bad.

33:42.540 --> 33:44.280
It's just…

33:44.650 --> 33:46.730
his line of work seems a bit dangerous.

33:48.270 --> 33:49.550
Oh, Mom,

33:49.570 --> 33:51.100
we're not kids anymore.

33:51.130 --> 33:52.750
Do you think we wouldn't have

33:52.830 --> 33:53.910
thought about these things

33:54.010 --> 33:55.630
before deciding to be together?

33:56.190 --> 33:57.150
We don't need you

33:57.190 --> 33:58.390
to point that out for us.

33:58.710 --> 33:59.630
Don't worry.

33:59.650 --> 34:01.290
We'll figure it out

34:01.310 --> 34:02.490
and make it work.

34:02.550 --> 34:04.230
We'll be happy together.

34:04.710 --> 34:05.430
Now, lie down

34:05.450 --> 34:06.310
and get some sleep.

34:06.310 --> 34:07.440
It's so late.

34:07.550 --> 34:08.110
Go to sleep.

34:08.139 --> 34:09.320
You've got your checkup tomorrow, right?

34:11.380 --> 34:11.860
Come here.

34:13.739 --> 34:15.190
I've missed you so much.

34:18.760 --> 34:20.310
I've missed you.

34:20.980 --> 34:22.290
I've missed you too.

34:23.070 --> 34:24.030
Good girl.

34:52.620 --> 34:53.620
Are you asleep?

34:57.990 --> 34:58.780
Not yet.

35:04.120 --> 35:05.560
See you on the balcony.

35:10.440 --> 35:11.010
Okay.

35:21.570 --> 35:22.440
Are you cold?

35:22.670 --> 35:23.310
Not really.

35:24.800 --> 35:25.770
Is your mom asleep?

35:28.860 --> 35:29.710
Don't take

35:29.710 --> 35:30.950
what my mom said to heart, okay?

35:30.970 --> 35:31.940
She's always like that.

35:32.010 --> 35:33.250
I'm fine.

35:33.510 --> 35:35.060
Your mom's visit was so sudden.

35:35.080 --> 35:36.490
I wasn't prepared at all.

35:37.070 --> 35:38.780
How was the food?

35:39.150 --> 35:40.030
It was amazing!

35:40.070 --> 35:40.910
The Stir-fried Beef

35:40.910 --> 35:41.910
was so good.

35:43.080 --> 35:45.880
What does your mom like for breakfast?

35:45.910 --> 35:47.050
I'll get up early and make it for her.

35:47.270 --> 35:47.710
No need.

35:47.760 --> 35:48.390
Tomorrow morning,

35:48.410 --> 35:50.170
I'm taking her to the hospital for her checkup.

35:50.200 --> 35:51.090
She can't eat breakfast.

35:51.190 --> 35:52.030
Don't worry about it.

35:53.460 --> 35:54.470
Then I'll take you guys there.

35:55.100 --> 35:55.840
Don't bother.

35:55.910 --> 35:57.310
She knows her way around the hospital better than you do.

36:02.030 --> 36:04.240
By the way, about what my mom said earlier,

36:04.310 --> 36:05.630
can you really do it?

36:06.210 --> 36:06.820
Do what?

36:07.670 --> 36:08.420
You know,

36:08.620 --> 36:10.130
take one step and come here.

36:13.480 --> 36:15.190
You don't want me anymore, huh?

36:17.870 --> 36:18.700
Then catch me.

36:18.760 --> 36:19.640
No problem.

36:20.760 --> 36:21.790
Get ready.

36:21.820 --> 36:22.500
-I'm coming.
-Come here.

36:33.060 --> 36:34.130
I'll head in.

36:34.420 --> 36:35.670
Go. Get some sleep.

36:37.310 --> 36:38.080
Goodnight.

36:42.400 --> 36:43.280
Goodnight.

36:49.190 --> 36:49.910
Goodnight.

36:59.050 --> 37:01.290
If he's Jiang, you've got nothing to worry about.

37:01.430 --> 37:02.650
Just accept him.

37:03.410 --> 37:04.560
If you don't,

37:04.580 --> 37:06.410
someone else will snatch him away.

37:07.070 --> 37:07.990
Dr. Han,

37:08.240 --> 37:09.850
you're a parent too.

37:10.030 --> 37:11.440
You can understand me, right?

37:11.550 --> 37:12.190
Of course,

37:12.320 --> 37:13.400
I understand completely.

37:13.590 --> 37:14.190
I know

37:14.210 --> 37:14.710
you're here

37:14.750 --> 37:15.750
to check him out, aren't you?

37:16.000 --> 37:17.290
You've noticed it, haven't you?

37:17.350 --> 37:18.250
In this hospital,

37:18.430 --> 37:19.580
there are so many

37:19.680 --> 37:21.330
female doctors and nurses

37:21.350 --> 37:23.060
with their eyes on Jiang.

37:23.510 --> 37:25.010
If Lu Yan weren't so well-liked,

37:25.270 --> 37:25.980
someone

37:26.030 --> 37:27.560
would've gotten to him already.

37:30.530 --> 37:31.910
How long do you plan to evaluate him?

37:33.320 --> 37:33.870
Alright.

37:35.200 --> 37:36.000
Mrs. Lu,

37:36.420 --> 37:37.370
think about it.

37:37.480 --> 37:39.850
Captain Jiang is a police officer,

37:40.130 --> 37:41.820
and Lu Yan is a doctor.

37:41.860 --> 37:43.180
A cop and a doctor,

37:43.210 --> 37:44.720
doesn't that sound perfect?

37:46.790 --> 37:48.250
But they're both so busy,

37:48.610 --> 37:50.610
and their work schedules are irregular.

37:50.750 --> 37:52.180
Even if they're together,

37:52.800 --> 37:53.990
it's almost like

37:54.020 --> 37:54.990
a long-distance relationship.

37:55.100 --> 38:00.320
[Blood Test Station]

37:55.890 --> 37:57.190
I can't speak for anyone else,

37:57.270 --> 37:58.070
but Captain Jiang?

37:58.100 --> 37:58.780
He's 100%

37:58.810 --> 38:00.090
reliable.

38:00.550 --> 38:01.940
Every time Lu's in trouble,

38:01.960 --> 38:03.050
he's the first one

38:03.110 --> 38:03.870
to show up

38:03.870 --> 38:04.790
and protect her.

38:07.150 --> 38:08.360
Don't worry.

38:08.380 --> 38:09.380
Captain Jiang

38:09.460 --> 38:10.760
is a great guy.

38:12.190 --> 38:13.520
Don't worry, okay?

38:17.970 --> 38:18.860
Yilin,

38:19.200 --> 38:19.950
look,

38:20.000 --> 38:22.240
if they're so great together,

38:22.270 --> 38:23.880
why did they break up

38:23.900 --> 38:24.790
in the first place?

38:25.120 --> 38:26.830
Oh, you don't get it.

38:26.990 --> 38:29.350
They just rekindled their love.

38:30.480 --> 38:31.190
It's wonderful.

38:31.230 --> 38:32.190
Don't worry.

38:34.530 --> 38:36.430
Your blood pressure is a bit high.

38:39.240 --> 38:40.230
Let's stop talking.

38:40.480 --> 38:41.700
Take another reading.

38:41.830 --> 38:43.030
Sorry.

38:44.700 --> 38:45.430
Mom.

38:46.240 --> 38:47.660
The test results are out?

38:48.470 --> 38:49.190
Have some water.

38:50.070 --> 38:51.110
You're pouting again.

38:51.130 --> 38:52.600
What's bothering you this time?

38:55.270 --> 38:56.290
I've figured out

38:56.310 --> 38:57.790
what's going on here.

38:58.000 --> 38:59.030
Everyone

38:59.060 --> 39:00.780
at this hospital

39:01.050 --> 39:02.860
has been bought off by Jiang Chengyi.

39:02.940 --> 39:03.750
They're all

39:03.800 --> 39:05.070
singing his praises.

39:06.740 --> 39:07.960
What are they saying?

39:09.360 --> 39:11.350
They say he's decent,

39:11.380 --> 39:12.610
reliable,

39:12.790 --> 39:13.630
honest,

39:13.660 --> 39:14.320
and down-to-earth,

39:14.460 --> 39:15.870
and that all the doctors and nurses at this hospital

39:15.870 --> 39:16.950
like him.

39:17.650 --> 39:18.950
It's as if he's one in a million,

39:18.970 --> 39:20.120
and you'd regret missing out on him.

39:21.270 --> 39:22.220
Where is he now?

39:22.760 --> 39:24.050
At work.

39:24.080 --> 39:25.100
Call him.

39:25.490 --> 39:26.930
Ask him to pick us up later.

39:27.080 --> 39:28.770
Mom, come on.

39:29.100 --> 39:30.260
Relax.

39:30.530 --> 39:32.450
I won't give him a hard time.

39:33.980 --> 39:34.500
Fine,

39:34.520 --> 39:34.820
I'll call him later.

39:36.450 --> 39:37.160
Call him now.

39:37.240 --> 39:38.440
Let me check the results first.

39:38.480 --> 39:39.600
Call him now.

39:39.620 --> 39:40.530
Later, I promise.

39:46.400 --> 39:48.460
[I'd like to explain it to you in person.]

39:46.400 --> 39:48.460
[Got time to have lunch with me? About what happened last time—]

40:06.370 --> 40:07.140
Open the door.

40:29.250 --> 40:29.900
Get in the car.

40:29.920 --> 40:30.520
Come on.
